Validate Resolved Bugs for December Release

Description

Validate all bugs marked as resolved for the December release to ensure fixes work as expected and no regressions are introduced. Each bug fix must be verified against its original issue, and functionality should behave correctly across impacted areas.

Acceptance Criteria

Given all December release bugs are marked as resolved,
When validation is performed for each bug fix,
Then all fixes should function correctly without reoccurrence of the issues or any new regressions.

Validate Snyk Issues After Resolution

Description

Validate all previously identified Snyk security issues to ensure that the applied fixes are effective. Confirm that no vulnerabilities reappear and that the system functions correctly after the security updates.

Acceptance Criteria

Given the Snyk issue fixes are deployed,
When validation is performed,
Then all reported vulnerabilities should be resolved and no new security issues should be introduced.
